<title>UK: Card Clear has 65 pct of Cardcast.</title>
<headline>Card Clear has 65 pct of Cardcast.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-10-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Card Clear Plc said on Thursday it owns 64.6 percent of Cardcast and was extending its offer for the company to October 24.</p>
<p>The two companies announced on August 22 that they had agreed to merge in a move that valued Cardcast at about 15.4 million stg.</p>
<p>The two firms specialise in combatting the fraudulent use of stolen or lost credit and cheque cards.</p>
